quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  60,6,"Woodaniina mon e maֹ“ֹ“e ֳ±eemtanirgal moֶ´ֶ´al wonande oon joortiiֹ—o e Alla e ֳ±alngu laakara, oon ֹ—uurniiֹ—o noon Pellet Alla ko gala jettaaֹ—o"
  60,7,"Yaama nde Alla waֹ—ata hakkunde mon e ֹ“een ֹ“e ngaֳ±andirֹ—on gilli, Alla ko kattanֹ—o Alla ko kafroowo bakkatuuji jurmotooֹ—o"
  60,8,Alla haֹ—ataa mon ֹ“een ֹ“e kaֹ“aani e mon e diine ֹ“e njaltinaani mon e galleeji mon nde ֹ—iggantonֹ“e nuunֹ—on faade e maֹ“ֹ“e pellet Alla ko jiֹ—ֹ—o nuunֹ—uֹ“e
  60,9,"Kono Alla haֹ—ata mon ko ֹ“een haֹ“atooֹ“e mon e diine yaltinooֹ“e mon galleeji mon ֹ“e mballandiri e yaltinde mon, nde keetnaton ֹ“e kala baֹ—ֹ—o ֹ“e keeda ko ֹ“een ngoni tooֳ±ooֹ“e"
  60,10,"Eehey mon goonֹ—inֹ“e si goonֹ—inֹ“e rewֹ“e ngarii e mon njaribeeֹ“e Alla na anndi iimaan mum en, si on nganndii koֹ“e goonֹ—inֹ“e wotee ndutteeֹ“e e heeferֹ“e ֹ“e ndaganaaki heeferֹ“e ֹ“e heeferֹ“e ֹ“e kadi ndaganaaki ֹ“e, totteeֹ“e koֹ“e nafqi ko bakkaat alah e mon nde ndesaton ֹ“e si on tottii ֹ“e teֵ‹e maֹ“ֹ“e wote nanngite piֹ“le rewֹ“e heeferֹ“e naamnee ko nafquֹ—on kamֹ“e ne yo ֹ“e naamna ko ֹ“e nafqi ko, ko ֹ—uum woni ֳ±aawoore Alla hakkunde mon Alla ko gannda ֳ±eeֳ±ֹ—uֹ—o"
  60,11,Si huunde faatiima mon e rewֹ“e mon faade e heefereeֹ“e leptuֹ—on ֹ“e tottee ֹ“een ֹ“e rewֹ“e mum en njahi fotde koֹ“e tottirno kulee Alla mbo goonֹ—in ֹ—on O
